OL,5, Female BBC employees who were harassed 
OL,6, online by former radio presenter Alex  
OL,7, Belfield have accused the corporation  
OL,8, of failing to help them.               
OL,10,FThe BBC is conducting an internal      
OL,11,Freview "to establish what lessons can  
OL,12,Fbe learned", but the women want an     
OL,13,Findependent investigation or review.   
OL,15,FBelfield, from Nottingham, was jailed  
OL,16,Fin September for stalking four men,    
OL,17,Fincluding presenter Jeremy Vine.       
OL,19,FThe jury found him not guilty of       
OL,20,Fstalking the four other complainants.  
